    ###
    ###  Neahttadigisánit maintainer tasks
    ###

    Updating FSTs
    
        compile FSTs for the relevant languages locally
	    copy to the relevant bin catalogue under opt

    Updating dictionaries
    
        $ fab PROJECT update-dicts
    
    Compiling new dictionaries (remember to update first)
    
        $ fab PROJECT compile-dicts
    
    Updating translation strings
    
        $ fab PROJECT compile-strings
    
    Testing configuration (run before restart, always)

        $ fab PROJECT test-configuration
    
    Restarting services
    
        $ fab PROJECT restart-service

    Adding stem information to sme-nob.all.xml 

        $ fab add-stem2dict
    
    Find a language
    
        $ fab where-is --iso:ISO
